title: Number of homicides in Sweden 2008 to 2018
summary: Overall Number of homicides has increased over the Year.
Number of homicides is slightly increasing from 2011 to 2013, roughly constant from 2013 to 2014, rapidly increasing from 2014 to 2015, and lastly roughly constant from 2015 to 2017.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum Number of homicides, about 113.0 was reported at Year 2017
Minimum Number of homicides about 68.0 was reached at Year 2012
